  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and sauté until fragrant.",
    "Add green beans and cook until just tender but still crisp.",
    "Season with thyme, paprika, red pepper flakes, oregano, and white wine vinegar. Stir well to coat the vegetables.",
    "Place salmon fillets in the pan, skin side up. Cover with a lid and simmer for about 8 minutes on low heat.",
    "Remove from heat and let it rest for 2-3 minutes before serving.",
    "Drizzle almond milk over the cooked salmon, garnish with Parmesan cheese if desired."
